  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>2-4-2026</strong> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">This game is currently going through a major revision and a public playtest.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The default branch is not the current / correct version.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">I want to confirm the game is stable before making the full release official. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">If you are interested in testing the new version of the game, please message me on Discord - Link in store description</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Wishlist if you prefer to be alerted when the official version is released.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Thank you for being patient while I get this sorted out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>2-4-2026</strong> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">This game is currently going through a major revision and a public playtest.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The default branch is not the current / correct version.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">I want to confirm the game is stable before making the full release official. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">If you are interested in testing the new version of the game, please message me on Discord - Link in store description</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Wishlist if you prefer to be alerted when the official version is released.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Thank you for being patient while I get this sorted out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
